{"tid":929380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川巴士爆炸車窗震碎 網傳乘客上車點火片","createTime":"2018-12-05T13:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T17:22:12.000Z","uid":6497,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e248ae0533d3c309f7a1fce01ebc383e0e7d65c6","tid":929380,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"（更新：內容）四川省樂山市一部巴士，今日下午5時許突然爆炸，車廂的玻璃全部爆裂，事故造成最少17人受傷，當局正在調查事件原因。網上流傳的影片顯示，一名男子手持疑似爆炸品上車，一上車之後馬上燃點，扔入車廂，然後爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是樂山市一部行走3號線巴士，下午5時半駛至夾江縣時突然爆炸，現場拍到的影片顯示爆炸發生後巴士冒出白煙，而且車上的玻璃全部震碎。<br />\n<br />\n網上廣傳的影片是來自巴士上的閉路電視，時間與發生爆炸的時間吻合。片段顯示巴士在車站上客，其他乘客上車後，一名手持疑似爆炸品的男子上車，上車後他拿出打火機燃點，然後扔入車廂，隨即發生爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n當地消息指，事故造成最少17人受傷，已送到當地醫院救治，事故原因正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181205/large/1544014953_80d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181205%2Flarge%2F1544014953_80d8.jpg&h=5a77a952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181205/large/1544014953_063c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181205%2Flarge%2F1544014953_063c.jpg&h=f3d5fb7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAllahu akbar<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a3525c147d7b264b439c047dff64765226f8e2","tid":929380,"uid":180576,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"RUN (響起BGM)"},{"pid":"0bdee23d690967676980c27faa7e101e4b950a2c","tid":929380,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AstywsA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F